reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great and convenient
reviews.reviewText: Was a little skeptical at first on the quality, but these are very sturdy and easy to mount. They are making things so much easier for My Wife's sewing/Craft room. Might get another one for my office.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Much easier to use than getting down under desk
reviews.reviewText: This bolts right to your desk - really handy to save from having to go under the desk all the way in back to get to the power strip. Has usb an and usb c ports as well so versatile for charging needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Does the job well.
reviews.reviewText: This product is very well made and does the job well. Would recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great power strip
reviews.reviewText: This is a great little power strip I purchased during a "Lightning Deal" during Prime Days for $30. While that is a bit pricey, I needed a power strip to attach to a metal desk frame and this works perfectly. I do like that the outlets are spaced far enough apart so I can utilize all outlets when some of the plugs are the larger brick type. This model comes with 3 outlets, 2 USB-A, and 2 USB-C outlets. The USB outlets are quick charging. They do offer a 5 outlet power strip as well. The clamp securely attaches to the frame and does not move when unplugging cords. Of note...the product description says it is a surge protector and the box says "overcurrent protection" with no mention on level of protection. Overall, pleased with this purchase.Update: Taking one star off as the USB outlet does not always work with the little light I use at the desk. I have to use a brick and take up an outlet when using the light.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect addition to Vari standing desk!
reviews.reviewText: I have bought a Vari standing desk and cable management system from amazon, however the issue with their cable management system is that large plugs like macbook pro chargers will not fit.This was a cheap and awesome fix for my issue, its also more convenient when I need to unplug it for on the go use.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great product, works as advertised! This power extension is exactly what I was looking for to solve for quick and immediate desktop charging. Phones, laptops and gaming systems. It does stick up and take space but it’s a good trade off and I knew that going into it. Recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Absolutely love this thing!
reviews.reviewText: Mounted it on my desk and haven’t hardly thought about it since. It fits in so seamlessly that I forget it’s a separate accessory sometimes. Excellent power delivery even when all plugs and ports are in use, and having extra USB-C ports available without a block is super convenient. I’ll likely be picking up more of these in the future!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024

reviews.reviewText: I like the look and functionality of this product. The main power cable is not strong enough to bend or have any pressure. it will stop working, so don’t bend it or push it against a wall.
Fits great on bottom of the couch for easy reach for chargers
